{"tid":882623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"偷懶扶巴士前進　單車少年過彎一摔遭輾殺","createTime":"2018-10-30T09:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T09:49:35.000Z","uid":75969,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b2820b91642ef27dea5b5c338dcb0f37ee273f5a","tid":882623,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:02:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181030/640_7c9ed6ce3bd7894cb4b33c709983dea6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181030%2F640_7c9ed6ce3bd7894cb4b33c709983dea6.jpg&h=ba4d509f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n車輪的致命接觸！巴西一名15歲少年，日前與同伴騎單車行經聖保羅州瓜魯柳斯時，他偷懶「搭便車」扶著一輛公車前行，但當公車右轉時，公車前輪與單車後輪發生碰撞，少年失去重心摔車，隨即遭到公車輾斃。<br />\n<br />\n有網友將拍下恐怖瞬間的監視器畫面分享到《Live Leak》網站，影片顯示，事發在10月24日下午5時許，當時單車少年左手搭著公車前行，卻沒留意到過彎時兩車距離變近，隨即公車右前輪撞到單車後輪，少年摔趴在地，連人帶車被捲入車底後，又被公車右後輪輾過，公車緊急停車，同伴也趕緊下車察看，但單車少年斃命當場。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181030/640_a70cc0865e6ef16d803a51e42a375a43.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181030%2F640_a70cc0865e6ef16d803a51e42a375a43.jpg&h=399c90f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181030/640_024471a17d3c7db830639b4ac5466976.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181030%2F640_024471a17d3c7db830639b4ac5466976.jpg&h=22e2e805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181030/1456595/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181030%2F1456595%2F&d=%2Bi4EYpcX0ygC0tY6g2C%2Fs6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=6bd64810\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181030%2F1456595%2F&h=6e540a1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181030/1456595/</a>"},{"pid":"2bb57fbab6209e14819608585ecf43abc3222b09","tid":882623,"uid":167506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b664fba8e1160a75d2921d4fedec29c97e6ed30","tid":882623,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:13:55.000Z","msg":"d人真係同支國差唔多"},{"pid":"477b8bcc6d48e4fa4c075b4b41094099bd1dd101","tid":882623,"uid":43721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:46:27.000Z","msg":"扶前面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b77858618459ffc48d8dc5645d993de5af2265c","tid":882623,"uid":167506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b664fba8e1160a75d2921d4fedec29c97e6ed30","tid":882623,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:13:55.000Z","msg":"d人真係同支國差唔多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:49:35.000Z","msg":"同一人種"}]}